name: Chel Dorado
description:
This time it's Chel from El Dorado.

Trained at 3700 steps, I also included I nude reference using her model sheet.

So far It mimics the exact style from El Dorado. I haven't have any problems with her so far.

You will need to add "1girl, barefoot, (thin waist), (black_hair), dark-skinned_female, dark_skin, earrings, jewelry, long_hair" To get the best experience. To even get exact, you could leave the lora weight at 1.
